            Disputes are accepted for the <strong>previous week only</strong>. Fill in your details below &mdash; your submission will be logged automatically and <strong>both you and HR will receive a confirmation email</strong>.
          </div>
          <div id="d-no-week" style="display:none;padding:14px;text-align:center;background:rgba(251,191,36,.08);border-radius:9px;border:1px solid rgba(251,191,36,.25);color:var(--ascend);font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:10px;">
